				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				This and Fleshripper are actually not that hard to get if you have a high level friend or are not afraid of dying. :)  If you can make it to Sol B without dying,(try friday nights, everything down there is camped) occasionally someone will put out an ooc or a shout that someone can come loot it because either they can't use it or they don't want it.  It is found off a kobold that was lvl 32 when i asked,(sorry, didn't catch the name) and i also found out that the proc doesn't go off until you are 10 lvls below the monster that drops it. I guess that the proc will kick in at lvl 22 even though I am only 15 at the present.  But it is only a lvl 9 cleric spell and the stats on the sword are better than the Langseax and dual-wielding this with a crystalline blade dishes out a lot of damage in a hurry. Great weapon, not to hard to get if you have patience.<BR>
